{{作品名稱|name=''Crazy Heart''|hk=聲聲相識|tw=瘋狂的心|equiv-cn=tw}}是一部2009年[[史考特·库伯|史考特·库伯]]编剧并执导的美国剧情片，改编自1987年[[Thomas_Cobb|Thomas Cobb]]所写的同名小说<ref name=bookCrazyHeart>{{cite book |author=Cobb, Thomas |title=Crazy Heart |url=https://archive.org/details/crazyheart0000cobb |publisher=Harper & Row |location=San Francisco |year=1987 |pages= |isbn=0-06-015803-4 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>，同名小说根据乡村歌手[[Hank_Thompson|Hank Thompson]]的真实经历写成<ref name='Lewis2009'>{{cite web | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2009/12/hank-thompson-crazy-hearts-reallife-bad-blake.html | title = Hank Thompson: 'Crazy Heart's' real-life Bad Blake | accessdate = 2010-07-06 | last = Lewis | first = Randy | date = 2009-12-28 | work = Los Angeles Times | archive-date = 2018-06-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180623221944/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2009/12/hank-thompson-crazy-hearts-reallife-bad-blake.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。男主角[[杰夫·布里吉斯|杰夫·布里吉斯]]的演出获得2009年[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|奥斯卡最佳男主角奖]]，音乐人 Bingham 和 Burnett 因歌曲“The Weary Kind”获得[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖]]。

影片预算700万美圆，最初打算制作成一部直接发行DVD的作品<ref name='Cieply2009'>{{cite news | author=[[Michael_Cieply|Cieply, Michael]] | coauthors= | authorlink= | title=A Surprise Gets Buzz for Oscars | date=2009-11-18 | publisher=The New York Times Company | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/19/movies/19crazy.html?_r=1 | work=The New York Times | pages= | accessdate=2010-01-26 | language= | archive-date=2014-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141106100425/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/19/movies/19crazy.html?_r=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name='Honeycutt2009'>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/film-reviews/Crazy+Heart+--+Film+Review-1004048527.story |title=Crazy Heart -- Film Review |accessdate=2010-02-27 |last=Honeycutt |first=Kirk |date=2009-11-29 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100226132324/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/film-reviews/Crazy%20Heart%20--%20Film%20Review-1004048527.story |archivedate=2010-02-26 }} </ref>，后来改由[[Fox_Searchlight_Pictures|Fox Searchlight Pictures]]发行于2009年12月16日上映<ref>{{cite web | url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/2009/11/04/oscar_watch_crazy_hearts_bridges_joins_actors_fray/ | title=Oscar Watch: 'Crazy Heart''s Bridges Joins Actors Fray | publisher=Anne Thompson/Blogs.IndieWire.com | accessdate=2009-11-04 | archive-date=2009-11-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091107135910/http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/2009/11/04/oscar_watch_crazy_hearts_bridges_joins_actors_fray/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://content.foxsearchlight.com/inside/node/3656 |title=Fox Searchlight Pictures Acquires 'Crazy Heart' |publisher=Content.FoxSearchlight.com |accessdate=2009-07-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090724074324/http://content.foxsearchlight.com/inside/node/3656 |archivedate=2009-07-24 }}</ref>。

==剧情==
Blake曾是一名叱咤风云的[[乡村音乐|乡村音乐]][[创作歌手|创作歌手]]，然而日渐变老的他却肆意消耗着自己的人生显得日益穷困潦倒，女记者Jean决心帮助他重新在舞台上焕发光彩。

